name: PowerShell Utilities
description:
Collection of automation scripts which wraps various built-in Powershell cmdlets for use in XSOAR.

CalculateTimeSpan - Calculates the span of time between two dates.
VersionEqualTo - Test if a version number is the same as another version number.
VersionGreaterThan - Test if a version number is greater than another version number.
VersionLessThan - Test if a version number is less than another version number.
author: Oliver Li
